Fluid Textures wallpapers
=========================

Source: Microsoft Design (https://microsoft.design/wallpapers/)

These wallpapers are created and owned by Microsoft. They are redistributed
here for use as desktop backgrounds in unity-shell.

Microsoft's wallpapers page does not attach an explicit open-source license to
the images. All rights to the artwork remain with Microsoft Corporation. They
are offered for personal desktop use; the images are not modified.

If you are the rights holder and object to this redistribution, please open an
issue on the unity-backgrounds repository and the files will be removed.
